# ============================================================================
# .gitignore - STT-TTS-STS Application
# ============================================================================
# This file excludes unnecessary files from version control to keep the
# repository clean and minimal for public distribution.
#
# INCLUDED (tracked by git):
#   - Source code (.py, .ts, .tsx)
#   - Configuration templates (.env.example)
#   - Documentation (README.md, DEPLOYMENT_GUIDE.md)
#   - Package files (requirements.txt, package.json)
#   - Essential data files (data/terms.json, data/voice_aliases.json)
#
# EXCLUDED (not tracked by git):
#   - Database files (.db)
#   - Environment files with secrets (.env)
#   - Build artifacts and compiled files
#   - IDE/editor specific files
#   - Logs, cache, temporary files
#   - User-specific data
# ============================================================================

